The evidence with the title 'CEO pay continues to rise as typical workers are paid less ... ' says Jun 12, 2014  ... Trends in ceo compensation last year : average ceo compensation was $15.2 million in 2013 , using a comprehensive measure of ceo pay that covers CEOs of the top 350 U.S. firms and includes the value of stock options exercised in a given year , up 2.8 percent since 2012 and 21.7 percent since 2010 . 
